title: Leading YouTube content categories of female U.S. Millennials 2016
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Share of views for 11 number of Youtube Categoriess.
The Share of views is highest at Youtube Categories Beauty and style and lowest at Youtube Categories Food and drink.
The maximum Youtube Categories Beauty and style has got 62.0 times higher Share of views than the minimum Youtube Categories Food and drink.
